# Dashboard APIs

Dashboard APIs provide financial analytics and summaries.

---

## Get Financial Summary

Returns total income, total expenses, and net balance.

Endpoint

```
GET /api/dashboard/summary
```

Access Level

Viewer, Analyst, Admin

Response

```
{
  "totalIncome": 20000,
  "totalExpense": 8000,
  "balance": 12000
}
```

---

## Category Summary

Returns total expenses grouped by category.

Endpoint

```
GET /api/dashboard/category-summary
```

Response

```
[
  {
    "category": "food",
    "total": 2000
  },
  {
    "category": "shopping",
    "total": 3000
  }
]
```

---

## Recent Transactions

Returns the most recent financial transactions.

Endpoint

```
GET /api/dashboard/recent
```

Response

```
[
  {
    "_id": "transaction_id",
    "amount": 500,
    "type": "expense",
    "category": "food",
    "date": "2026-04-01"
  }
]
```

---

# Error Responses

Validation Error

```
{
  "error": "Invalid input data"
}
```

Unauthorized Request

```
{
  "error": "Unauthorized"
}
```

Forbidden Access

```
{
  "error": "Access denied"
}
```

